Login using a developer ID. Using CloudFormation service, design a template to create a VPC with Auto Scaling and Elastic Load Balancing in Oregon region.

User inputs: VPC and Subnet, Availability Zone, Key Pair, SSH rule, Instance type, Instance count, Region, AMI ID, Security group

Output: Website URL
Deploy a simple PHP application with database support in server stack using AMI. Database details should be read from an 'dbConnectionDetails.ini' file placed within an S3 bucket.

Use the template to deploy similar set up in North Virginia and N.California regions. Input parameters should be configured appropriately to accommodate the region change
